OL,6,FA "dangerous" rapist who threatened
OL,7,Fhis former partner with boiling water
OL,8,Fhas been handed a "significant" jail
OL,9,Fsentence in what has been described as
OL,10,F"one of the worst cases of abuse seen
OL,11,Fby police".
OL,13,FBen Fitton isolated Hannah - who has
OL,14,Fwaived her right to anonymity -
OL,15,Fdestroyed her clothes, threatened her
OL,16,Fwith violence and on one occasion left
OL,17,Fher with a significant knee injury
OL,18,Fwhich required surgery.
