OL,6,FThe 33-year-old, from Glossop,
OL,7,FDerbyshire, was "consumed by jealousy,
OL,8,Fparanoia, and anger" and subjected
OL,9,FHannah to a campaign of sexual,
OL,10,Fphysical, emotional, and psychological
OL,11,Fabuse over a two-year period which
OL,12,Fleft her in "constant fear."
OL,14,FOn one occasion, Fitten had threatened
