OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read out
OL,7,Fat Manchester Crown Court on
OL,8,FWednesday, 14 February, Hannah said
OL,9,Fher abuser had tried to "destroy"
OL,10,Fevery aspect her of life and that she
OL,11,Fnow finds it "difficult to let anybody
OL,12,Fin."
OL,14,FFitton, of no fixed abode, was found
OL,15,Fguilty in September 2024 of two counts
OL,16,Fof rape, non-fatal strangulation,
OL,17,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour and
OL,18,Fcausing grievous bodily harm.
