OL,7,Fan additional three years on extended
OL,8,Flicense due to the "significant risk"
OL,9,Fthe judge deemed he posed. He was also
OL,10,Fissued a restraining order.
OL,12,F"Everything I had worked for, being a
OL,13,Fgood mother, being strong and
OL,14,Findependent and building friendship
OL,15,Fgroups and good relationships with my
OL,16,Ffamily, was suddenly gone, Ben took
OL,17,Fthat away from me," Hannah said in her
