OL,6,F"Me and my family have agreed to move
OL,7,Fon and forgive each other for the
OL,8,Fthings that happened but it remains
OL,9,Fdifficult on both sides.
OL,11,F"One of the things Ben set out to do
OL,12,Fwas to destroy my relationship with my
OL,13,Ffamily and friends and both me and my
OL,14,Ffamily are determined to show him that
OL,15,Fhe failed.
OL,17,F"He didn't get my son taken from me
OL,18,Fand he hasn't broken us as a family.
OL,19,FHe doesn't get to have that over us.
