OL,7,Fto be very difficult for me as I now
OL,8,Fconstantly feel like people are trying
OL,9,Fto control me over the slightest
OL,10,Flittle thing and if anybody speaks out
OL,11,Fof turn to me, I immediately challenge
OL,12,Fthem and tell them not to talk to me
OL,13,Flike that.
OL,15,F"I just don't feel the same anymore, I
OL,16,Fused to be fluffy and soft, but I am
OL,17,Fvery hard faced now when it comes to
OL,18,Fother people. I find it difficult to
OL,19,Flet anybody in.
