OL,9,Fhe has me. I truly hope that nobody
OL,10,Felse will ever have to go through what
OL,11,FI have been through."
OL,13,FAfter the sentencing, Detective
OL,14,FConstable Russ Clarke, of Greater
OL,15,FManchester Police (GMP), said the
OL,16,Flevels of abuse Hannah endured "are
OL,17,Fthe worst I have ever seen in my time
OL,18,Fat GMP."
